{"type":null,"faqId":45913,"title":"微信发送的语音只能听到前几秒的语音（3~4s）？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:0.28125in;margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:0.5416667in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>请您确认手机是否安装了360智键，该应用目前与微信语音存在冲突，导致听到的语音不全。请卸载360智键程序，并将插在耳机孔上的智能按键设备卸下即可。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如果没有外接设备，请确认以下事项：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1、通过音量键调节“媒体音量”，确保音量大于零格。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2、确认在已开启微信的录音权限，操作路径：设置-全部设置-权限管理(隐私和安全)-应用-微信-信任此应用，开启即可。如下图：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=170011\" style=\"width:2.5618055in;height:4.272917in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=170012\" style=\"width:2.51875in;height:4.26875in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span>3、确认已关闭微信设置项“使用听筒播放语音”，操作路径：进入微信-我-设置-聊天-使用听筒播放语音，关闭即可。如下图：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>    </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=170013\" style=\"width:2.801389in;height:4.632639in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=170014\" style=\"width:2.76875in;height:4.6493053in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":139,"faqType":"应用程序管理","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1693","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Application-Management","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1444375537000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":10,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"不兼容,沃市场","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}